        <mxCell id="lg_arrows" value="Solid arrow = synchronous request-time call   ·   Dashed arrow = optional / cache / background propagation   ·   Arrow colour matches the source layer.&#10;Every edge uses orthogonal routing.  Cross-row edges are routed through &quot;buses&quot; in the gaps between rows so they never cross a box.&#10;The admin → gate dashed line is routed up the far-left margin (x=20) to clear all primitive and data-store boxes." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=18;spacingTop=4;fontColor=#3D4A5C" vertex="1" parent="1">
